Exhibit P-7
Andrew Gutentag to Taylor Lavery– March 7, 2019

[Gutentag]
How would it be if I quit but I didn't take the job there
```
```
[Lavery]
You can do whatever you want obviously
```
```
[Gutentag]
I know
```
```
[Gutentag]
But I still want to get paid.
```
```
[Lavery]
For?
```
```
[Gutentag]
Well u guys have a good amount on the table
```
```
[Lavery]
Oh so if you walk away how do you expect to get that
```
```
[Gutentag]
I mean technically I'd be fired because I won't sign it
